         //to convert a string into byte[] array.  here is used with the correct password digest which matches what was hard-coded in our CredentialsValidator constructor   this will provide us information about how to validate user's credentials against known values//    }      char []passwordInBytes= md.digest(correctPasswordDigest); //this line of code converts a string into byte[] array 
